          "type": "text",
          "order": 3,
          "text": "No other acute intracranial abnormalities."
        },
        {
          "id": "act_1776661495669_5wai",
          "type": "command",
          "order": 4,
          "commandId": "go_to_section",
          "params": {
            "sectionName": "impression"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "act_1776298073754_nzpj",
          "type": "text",
          "order": 5,
          "text": "No evidence of ischemic stroke as clinically queried and no acute intracranial abnormalities. \nMRI has decreased sensitivity for small or early infarcts. Clinical correlation is recommended. Can repeat MRI in approximately 24 hours including coronal DWI if there is ongoing clinical concern for stroke."
        }
      ],
      "isSystem": false
    },
    {
